{"tid":2257130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共電子偵察機昨晚深夜入侵台灣防空識別區 台灣空軍派出2架經國號戰機升空監視並警戒","createTime":"2020-10-25T02:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T03:38:21.000Z","uid":292499,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"74c9a8602078730a8a18be709f76c5c7ea232458","tid":2257130,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n軍方低調回應，昨晚確有中國軍機在台海附近空域活動，因為有其他基地戰機準備返航，基於輪流執勤原則，空軍作戰部調派台南基地2架IDF到台海空域警戒因應，是正常的升空警戒勤務，並無特殊或擦槍走火的突發狀況。<br />\n...<br />\n24日晚間飛臨的中國軍機據傳是空警2000（電偵機），我國空軍必然謹慎以對，不容對方侵門踏戶到我國空域偵察國防情報。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3331585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3331585&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=6d10b1cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3331585&h=04a09c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3331585</a>"},{"pid":"7855c68ffc79280408213e2d21761ae8aec16e7e","tid":2257130,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea32ccf9fcb2735095181311b268b1de4fe75968","tid":2257130,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8db4e2630f9beff3155e86286f5899144b9bd7f","tid":2257130,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"小小支那 可笑可笑"},{"pid":"cb0c62d477b111d92c477abb0a2203e54e33a782","tid":2257130,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike